name: Kiyohime 9in1 (Fate Grand Order) (FGO 清姬)
description:
LoRA of Kiyohime in FGO, works between 0.7-1.0

FGO清姬的模型，推荐权重0.7-1.0

-

Supports 9 sets of Official Outfits in total, 3 sets for Berserker class + 3 sets for Lancer class + 3 sets of Craft Essences.

支持共计9套官方外观，B阶3套+L阶3套+礼装外观3套

-

Berserker1=Berserker1, Aqua Kimono

Berserker2=Berserker2, Kiyohime kimono 2

Berserker3=Berserker3, black kimono, black horns, white hair, red eyes

Lancer1=Lancer1, yellow bra

Lancer2=Lancer2, one-piece swimsuit

Lancer3=Lancer3, blue bikini

Kiyohime in Ribbons-缎带附清姬=((InRibbon)), ribbon clothing

The Faithful Dog Who Waits-忠犬蓄势待发=FaithfulDog, puppy Kiyohime

Jurassic Dream-侏罗纪之梦=JurassicDream, aqua shorts

-

Feel free to post any idea or character model request in the Discussion

有模型的需求可以B站私信或者在这里留言给我

有空就会做
